Interface QueryBuilderInterface<QueryT>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReportQueryInterface.BuilderInterface, ServiceQueryInterface.BuilderInterface<PageT,SortOrderT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueryBuilder, ReportQuery.Builder, ServiceQuery.Builder, ServiceQuery.Builder, ServiceQueryBuilderImpl, ServiceQueryBuilderImpl

    public interface QueryBuilderInterface<QueryT>
    A builder for query objects.

    This builder is not thread safe.
